Question: There are more animals in the image on the right than in the image on the left.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2IubMCFt6FQ/VAccXRdoS0I/AAAAAAAAyn4/L-iITbexi54/s1600/7+(222).JPG

Right image URL: http://axarquiaviva.files.wordpress.com/2008/11/2843004647_1b0e6fb057.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many animals are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many animals are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} < {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
